candidates.title: v0.1.4
candidates.body:
changes:
- update ethers-rs to 2.0.14
- add support for trading on `mantle`
- update various builders/responses
- improve README

candidates.title: v0.1.3 w/ blast support
candidates.body:
major changes:
- add support for `BlastProd`
- include configs in binary so the sdk works in containerized environments 
- corresponding binding changes for mainnet contract changes

candidates.title: fix: configs directories work for crate
candidates.body:
changes:
- fix critical error where sdk downloaded from crates.io would fail to load config files correctly
- updated usdc quote address
- added id field to place order req/res
- formatted Cargo.toml
